# wd_project_26

# 🧠 Kidney Tumor Prediction (Deep Learning + MLOps)


An **end-to-end Deep Learning project** for **Kidney Tumor Prediction** using **CNN**, integrated with **MLOps**, **Docker**, and **AWS CI/CD pipeline**.


---


## 🚀 Project Overview


This project demonstrates how to build, version, track, and deploy a **Deep Learning-based medical imaging model** using modern **MLOps practices**.


### 🔑 Key Features
- CNN-based Kidney Tumor Prediction
- Modular & scalable project structure
- MLflow for experiment tracking
- DVC for data version control
- Flask API for inference
- Dockerized application
- AWS CI/CD pipeline (planned)


---


## 🛠️ Tech Stack


| Category | Tools |
|-------|------|
| Language | Python 3.10 |
| DL Framework | TensorFlow 2.16.1 |
| Data | NumPy, Pandas |
| Visualization | Matplotlib, Seaborn |
| MLOps | MLflow, DVC |
| Backend | Flask, Flask-CORS |
| DevOps | Docker, GitHub |
| Cloud | AWS (CI/CD) |


